stories.Title: Apple joins the Big Tech layoff
stories.Description: Despite trying to avoid following its Big Tech peers, Apple has eliminated some corporate retail team roles.

stories.Title: Meta is developing a new artificial intelligence model
stories.Description: This new model counts with the largest dataset of image annotations and it’s capable of identifying any kind of object in images and videos.

stories.Title: Google’s AI supercomputer is Nvidia A100 Chip new competitor
stories.Description: New details released by the company revealed that their supercomputer systems are 1.7 times faster and 1.9 times more power-efficient.

stories.Title: Virgin Orbit is now filling for bankruptcy
stories.Description: After suffering a major setback, the California-based company founded by Richard Branson is seeking buyers.

stories.Title: SpaceX's Starship Mars rocket is getting ready to lift off
stories.Description: SpaceX's massive Starship Mars rocket is preparing for its first-ever orbital attempt as early as next week, as they continue on their journey to reach the moon, Mars, and beyond.

stories.Title: Dawn Aerospace is launching a rocket-powered spaceplane
stories.Description: New Zealand's Dawn Aerospace has achieved an exciting development in space technology with the successful completion of the first three test flights of the Mk-II Aurora, a rocket-powered spaceplane

stories.Title: Artemis 2 crew is finally revealed by NASA
stories.Description: As we get ready for the first lunar mission since the Apollo program, NASA is finally announcing the four astronauts who will make history.

stories.Title: Kia is looking to expand their production in Europe
stories.Description: The firm has stated that its future EV production will expand beyond Gyeonggi, South Korea to core markets in Europe, China, US & India.

stories.Title: Bad news for developers with the new Safari 16.4
stories.Description: While a new Safari release may bring great news for standard Apple users, it can become a constant struggle for developers due to certain bugs.

stories.Title: Dogecoin reachs a new peak thanks to Twitter
stories.Description: The app's recent decision to replace its iconic blue bird logo with the viral Shiba Inu dog picture resulted in a sudden spike in its prices.

stories.Title: This french Startup is a great complement for Web3 and Web2 communities
stories.Description: To enhance engagement with their most passionate community members, companies can use Zealy's achievement system, which provides a more meaningful way to connect by implementing gamified tasks.

title: Meta's has a new AI model, SpaceX's new project is approaching, Apple couldn't avoid the lay-offs
